cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.DM, cs.CV, cs.CG

The paper deals with logical operators and their application to spatial reasoning, which suggests categories such as cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of mathematical morphology also suggests categories such as cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.CG (Computational Geometry). Finally, the mention of open sentences and sets of states suggests a connection to database theory and formal methods, which could place the paper in categories such as cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) or cs.DB (Databases).
